snippet.textDisplay: My niece didn’t we wouldn’t want her too. I try not to spoil her as I tend to have been guilty of that.  I have no kids.  She always is grateful 😇 She actually got a part time job and lost it due to. Lockdown her first little job she wanted so badly.  It is sad for some teens and small children they have missed out on so much.
